-al-qawl","tag-worldly-life-dunya"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-66S","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":34238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/06\/abdullah-except-dishonesty\/","url_meta":{"origin":23490,"position":0},"title":"Abdullah on Faith: Believers have many temperaments, except dishonesty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Yazid reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe believer may have all kinds of natural dispositions flowing throughout himself, except for treachery and dishonesty.\u201d Source: al-\u012ama\u0304n li-Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24910,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/31\/discuss-islam-hereafter-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":23490,"position":1},"title":"Hasan on Mosques: Only discuss Islam in the Masjid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 31, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Hazim reported: Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cA time will come to people when their discussions in the mosques will be about the affairs of their world. Allah has no need of it, so do not sit with them.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 34622\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38315,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/07\/akhlaq-sabr-samahah\/","url_meta":{"origin":23490,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Best Muslims have good character, patience, tolerance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 7, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: It was said to the Prophet, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, whose Islam is best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe patient and tolerant.\u201d It was said, \u201cWhich believers have the most complete faith?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThose with the best character.\u201d Source: al-Ima\u0304n li-Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 43 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35231,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/15\/ali-iman-light\/","url_meta":{"origin":23490,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Iman: Faith is a light in the heart, hypocrisy is darkness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 15, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Hind reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, faith begins like a fragment of white in the heart. Each time faith increases in magnitude, it increases that brightness. When he completes his faith, the entire heart is brightened. Verily, hypocrisy begins like a fragment in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34640,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/05\/masjid-home-every-taqi\/","url_meta":{"origin":23490,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Masajid: Mosques are the home of every righteous person","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe mosque is the home of every righteous person. Allah Almighty has guaranteed those who have their home in the mosques with the spirit, mercy, and safe passage over the bridge of Hell unto the pleasure\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24852,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/24\/ibn-masud-monk-forgiven-zina\/","url_meta":{"origin":23490,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Repentance: Monk forgiven for adultery by his charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 24, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Za'ra' reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cA monk worshiped Allah in his hermitage for sixty years. Then, a woman came and lay down at his side, so he lay down with her and was intimate with her for six nights. He became regretful\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"he